name: Fantasy Life Link! [3DS]
description:
Fantasy Life Link! is a RPG game developed by Level 5. It came out on 25-07-2013. Level 5 published the game.
Fantasy Life Link! is available on Nintendo 3DS.
It was produced by Akihiro Hino. It was directed by Atsushi Kanno. Nobuo Uematsu scored the game.
